"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-lifestyle-entertainment-paris-prepares-for-show-stopping-olympic-opening\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbEntertainment  ByAgence France Presse  3 minute read  18 June 2024  11:33 am  France's paralympic triple jumper Arnaud Assoumani in front of The Louvre Pyramide ahead of the Paris 2024 Olympic and Paralympic games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 29, \"end\": 35, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999948827924872, \"rank\": 3.665607567160087e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 89, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999948827924872, \"rank\": 3.665607567160087e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnaud_Assoumani\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arnaud Assoumani\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnaud_Assoumani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnaud_Assoumani\"}, {\"begin\": 150, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"score\": 0.9982976534645914, \"rank\": 0.0017052494608440535, \"text\": \"Louvre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: AFP  Music pounds through an empty hangar on the outskirts of Paris as dancers perform a few snatches of a top-secret routine in front of giant mirrors.\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.284257906844312e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Audiences will get to see the fruits of their labours on July 26 when the opening ceremony of theOlympic Gamesis held in Paris.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.284257906844312e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organisers promise something \\\"spectacular\\\" but their lips are sealed on the details.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A handful of journalists, including AFP, were able to attend just a few minutes of a rehearsal this month.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999982612735, \"rank\": 1.6755138663032668e-09, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Neon lights and disco balls contrasted with the industrial chaos of the decrepit but immense hangar.\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Such a huge space was necessary because - for the first time in Olympics history - the opening ceremony is not taking place in a stadium.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, it will stretch across seven kilometres of the River Seine with more than 3,000 dancers performing 10 different routines on the day.\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1007, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The section that AFP partly witnessed will include some 400, but nowhere is big enough for them to rehearse all at once so they work in smaller groups of around 50.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999982612735, \"rank\": 1.6755138663032668e-09, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It requires real organisation but we are getting there,\\\" said lead choreographer Maud Le Pladec.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There will not be a single bridge in Paris without some dancers on it,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.284257906844312e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her aim is to show dance in \\\"all its diversity\\\", bringing together everything from classical to breakdance.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the dancers' sneakers squeak around the floor, the head of the Olympics organising committee, Tony Estanguet, and the artistic director of the Games, Thomas Jolly, slip into the room to watch.\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1650, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 1706, \"end\": 1712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.8410864751810226, \"rank\": 0.18793573583911924, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Excellent, it makes you want to get involved!\\\"\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1797, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"said Estanguet.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No one is giving away any details, but Jolly says all the feasibility studies have been completed.\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The initial plan is going ahead with just a few minor modifications.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has taken concrete form since mid-March,\\\" said Jolly.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The choreographies are set, the costumes have come out of the workshops, the music.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are ready!\\\"\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NOW READ:Paris 2024 Olympics: Spreading love with condoms, but no champagne  Add The Citizen as a Preferred Source on Google and follow us on Google News to see more of our trusted reporting in Google News and Top Stories.\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2262, \"end\": 2268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9981714421210868, \"rank\": 0.0018274016358616322, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2286, \"end\": 2297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2338, \"end\": 2349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Download our app  Get the latest news and updates on Whatsapp  The latest news directly in your inbox  Support Local Journalism  2026 The Citizen.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2421, \"end\": 2429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Whatsapp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": []}]}"